=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/AppIconTopic_Finder.png\"></figure><h1>Stream audio and video from your Mac with AirPlay</h1><p>AirPlay lets you use a Wi-Fi connection to wirelessly <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=stream&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=GLOS3C9C9119&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0&amp;aside=true\" class=\"xRef Aside\">stream</a> music, videos, photos, and more from your Mac to your favorite speakers (such as HomePod mini), your Apple TV, and certain smart TVs. Just make sure your Mac and other devices are on the same Wi-Fi network.</p><figure><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/e99cc62e69896859fc7edb027d6ec71f.png\" alt=\"A Mac computer and devices to which it can stream content using AirPlay—for example, an Apple TV, HomePod mini speakers, and a smart TV.\" height=\"282\" width=\"466\" originalImageName=\"Art/S2224_AirPlayToDevices.png\"></figure><div id=\"mchl182e2b9a\" class=\"Subhead\"><h2 class=\"Name\">Listen to music on your favorite speakers</h2><p>Get that big band sound by streaming music from your Mac to a HomePod—or two—or any other AirPlay 2-enabled speaker. On your Mac, open the Apple Music app <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/644303d199b1bf61827a5854ae4867f8.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/AppIconTopic_Music.png\">, </span>queue your tunes, click <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/0557e2f2f629f2cb078f48ccffb55a9d.png\" alt=\"the AirPlay audio icon\" height=\"30\" width=\"31\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_AirPlayAudio.png\"> in the playback controls, then select a speaker. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=music&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MUSB58944D8F&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Use HomePod with Music on Mac</a>.</p><figure><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/447b850a5ab0b93464428397969b87f5.png\" alt=\"The playback controls in the Music app. The AirPlay audio icon is to the right of the volume slider.\" height=\"95\" width=\"214\" originalImageName=\"Art/S2222_AirPlayAudio.png\"></figure><div class=\"Alert\"><p class=\"Tip\"><strong class=\"tip\">Tip: </strong>Broaden your horizons during dinner by listening to your favorite travel podcast. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=podcasts&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=POD970198C2&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Listen to podcasts on Mac</a>.</p></div></div><div id=\"mchl76741cd2\" class=\"Subhead\"><h2 class=\"Name\">Play movies and more on the big screen</h2><p>It’s easy to play movies, TV shows, and videos on the big screen of your TV. On your Mac, open the Apple TV app <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/0d1fdd38d3aed20932fbc868af8ccc2e.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/AppIconTopic_TV.png\">, </span>start the show, click <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/8168b5a8526fb461574a8a18812d04c6.png\" alt=\"the AirPlay video icon\" height=\"30\" width=\"37\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_AirPlayVideo.png\"> in the playback controls, then select your Apple TV or smart TV. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=tvapp-mac&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=ATV31D6CAA7&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Control what’s playing in the Apple TV app on Mac</a>.</p><figure><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/7bab5f7d431f8b1dcb440c1247555457.png\" alt=\"The playback controls in the Apple TV app. The AirPlay video icon is below the progress bar.\" height=\"100\" width=\"232\" originalImageName=\"Art/S2220_AirPlayVideo.png\"></figure><div class=\"Alert\"><p class=\"Tip\"><strong class=\"tip\">Tip: </strong>Found a great video on the web you want to watch with your friends? Use AirPlay right in the Safari app. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=safari&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=IBRW27291639&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Play web videos in Safari on Mac</a>.</p></div></div><div id=\"mchlabcf8cb6\" class=\"Subhead\"><h2 class=\"Name\">Share photos with everyone in the room</h2><p>With AirPlay mirroring and your Apple TV, everyone in the room can view what’s playing on your Mac—like a slideshow of wedding photos in the Photos app—on your big screen TV. On your Mac, click Control Center <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/3045264ba38d067fcdf39c07a1129c88.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"26\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_ControlCenter.png\"> in the menu bar, click Screen Mirroring, then select your Apple TV or smart TV. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=stream-content-to-apple-tv&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MH40624&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Use AirPlay to stream what’s on your Mac to an HDTV</a>.</p><figure><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/f1adc4f958fa2e4d4c6e9dc730504e09.png\" alt=\"Screen mirroring options, including Apple TV, listed in Control Center.\" height=\"210\" width=\"385\" originalImageName=\"Art/S2204_ControlCenterMirroring.png\"></figure></div><p>If your Mac and other Apple devices support AirPlay to Mac, you can <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-your-mac-as-a-speaker&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL9A9776F2&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">listen to audio</a> and <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-your-mac-as-a-display&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL7D43ECB2&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">play video</a> from another device on your Mac. </p><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=quickly-change-settings&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL50F94F8F&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Use Control Center on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-homepod-with-mac&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL9BEEDD58&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Use HomePod with Mac</a><a href=\"https://www.apple.com/airplay/\" class=\"URL\">AirPlay website</a></div></body>","tags":[{"type":"audience","refKey":"PUBLIC_USERS","tagPath":"audience/PUBLIC_USERS","title":"Public"}]}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["IP-Meta/DesignVersion/DesignVersion2","platform/mac","DisplayVersion/macOS Ventura 13","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","ContentMode/liveContent","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexON","ArchivalStatus/Archived","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexOFF"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"SupportSearchIndexON","name":"SupportSearchIndexON","englishName":"SupportSearchIndexON","displayName":"SupportSearchIndexON","articleCount":"120736"},{"key":"liveContent","name":"Live Content","englishName":"Live Content","displayName":"Live Content","articleCount":"135880"},{"key":"IP-Meta","name":"IP-Meta","englishName":"IP-Meta","displayName":"IP-Meta","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ContentMode","name":"ContentMode","englishName":"ContentMode","displayName":"ContentMode","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"DesignVersion2","name":"DesignVersion 2","en